Subject: [PATCH] mei: fix error flow in probe
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Dismantle class device last in probe error flow to avoid accessing freed memory like:

